3260937/chinas-job-hungry-youth-offered-lifeline-south-korean-university-its-exemplary-employment-linked?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>韩国一所大学正在专门针对国际学生推出一个新的副学士学位课程，以应对劳动力和人口问题，其中一些问题也面临着中国的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3260937/chinas-job-hungry-youth-offered-lifeline-south-korean-university-its-exemplary-employment-linked?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官作证称，美国维持对台政策现状“至关重要”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261004/us-keeping-status-quo-taiwan-policy-vitally-important-senior-american-diplomat-testifies?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>盟友和合作伙伴表示，当他们了解华盛顿的立场主张“和平与稳定”时，他们会更愿意、更愿意与华盛顿站在一起。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261004/us-keeping-status-quo-taiwan-policy-vitally-important-senior-american-diplomat-testifies?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国尚未加入“富裕国家”俱乐部。中等收入陷阱已经出现了吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260891/china-has-yet-join-rich-country-club-has-middle-income-trap-been-sprung?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>关于中国将加入高收入国家行列的预测尚未取得成果。中等收入上限还有可能突破吗？还是一个重要的标杆吗？</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260891/china-has-yet-join-rich-country-club-has-middle-income-trap-been-sprung?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国议员获悉中国阻碍对新疆供应链进行准确审计</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261003/china-thwarts-accurate-audits-xinjiang-supply-chains-us-lawmakers-hear?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>拜登政府官员告诉美国国会及行政当局中国委员会，由于北京的故意举动，使用维吾尔人进行强迫劳动的情况不可能得到正确记录。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:47:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261003/china-thwarts-accurate-audits-xinjiang-supply-chains-us-lawmakers-hear?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的经济外交如何化解与菲律宾的紧张关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3260855/how-chinas-economic-diplomacy-can-defuse-tensions-philippines?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在军事化加剧的情况下，重返杜特尔特时代所谓的维护南沙群岛和平的协议对于菲律宾来说将是务实的一步。中国应该选择经济投资，而不是军事自信，这只会强化菲律宾人的负面舆论。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3260855/how-chinas-economic-diplomacy-can-defuse-tensions-philippines?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>对于哥伦比亚大学的华人来说，亲巴勒斯坦抗议激起了同情和恐惧</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261001/chinese-students-and-scholars-columbia-university-pro-palestinian-protests-evoke-sympathy-and-fear?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一位人士表示，决定是否参加示威活动充满了担忧，因为“现在在美国作为中国人已经很不稳定了”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261001/chinese-students-and-scholars-columbia-university-pro-palestinian-protests-evoke-sympathy-and-fear?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美日菲联盟加剧了北京在东海和南海的挑战</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260978/us-japan-philippines-alliance-adds-beijings-challenges-east-and-south-china-seas?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京与东京和马尼拉最近就争议岛屿发生对抗之际，两国正在加强与华盛顿的海上联盟。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:07:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260978/us-japan-philippines-alliance-adds-beijings-challenges-east-and-south-china-seas?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国对墨西哥的出口产品正面临更高的关税——这是否是更多关税的迹象？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260971/chinas-exports-mexico-are-getting-heavier-tariffs-it-sign-more-come?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着墨西哥对大多数中国进口产品征收新关税，观察人士和分析人士对于是否考虑采取更严格的措施存在分歧，但大多数人表示，来自美国的压力正在发挥作用。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 13:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260971/chinas-exports-mexico-are-getting-heavier-tariffs-it-sign-more-come?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国第二大短视频应用运营商快手关闭北京游戏项目进行重组</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3260969/chinas-no-2-short-video-app-operator-kuaishou-shuts-down-gaming-project-beijing-restructuring-move?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>快手科技解散其位于北京的视频游戏工作室后，约有 30 人被解雇。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 13:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3260969/chinas-no-2-short-video-app-operator-kuaishou-shuts-down-gaming-project-beijing-restructuring-move?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>当局要求航运远离禁区后，中国福建航母将进行首次海试</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3260964/chinas-fujian-aircraft-carrier-set-maiden-sea-trials-after-authorities-tell-shipping-stay-out?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>该舰是中国第一艘使用先进电磁弹射器的军舰，可以更频繁地发射战斗机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:47:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3260964/chinas-fujian-aircraft-carrier-set-maiden-sea-trials-after-authorities-tell-shipping-stay-out?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>以色列-加沙战争：中国外交部表示哈马斯和法塔赫承诺在北京会议后进行对话</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260961/israel-gaza-war-chinas-foreign-ministry-says-hamas-and-fatah-commit-dialogue-after-beijing-meeting?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据外交部发言人称，巴勒斯坦敌对政党在北京举行会议，“就促进内部和解进行深入、坦诚的对话”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:30:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260961/israel-gaza-war-chinas-foreign-ministry-says-hamas-and-fatah-commit-dialogue-after-beijing-meeting?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>由于经济放缓，消费者勒紧裤腰带，必胜客的中国所有者肯德基计划在中国“尚未开发”的小城市开设门店</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3260956/kfc-pizza-hut-owner-yum-china-plans-stores-countrys-untapped-smaller-cities-consumers-tighten-their?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中国大陆拥有肯德基和必胜客连锁餐厅的百胜中国控股公司计划在中国“未开发”地区开设更多门店，希望其低价策略能够吸引大量不太富裕的顾客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:30:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3260956/kfc-pizza-hut-owner-yum-china-plans-stores-countrys-untapped-smaller-cities-consumers-tighten-their?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>